properties.Name: InsurancePolicyEventType
properties.Description:
A type of event that may be associated with an insurance policy.

Ex:
- Insurance policy lapse
- Insurance policy issuance
- Insurance policy renewal
- Insurance policy cancellation
- Insurance policy review
- Insurance policy reinstatement

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyEventTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an insurance policy event type.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyEventTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of an insurance policy event type.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyEventTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an insurance policy event type.
